  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Allogene MSCs transplantation will be performed in patients with chronic liver diseases
      through portal vein by ultrasound guiding and therapeutic effects including short-term
      effects and long-term follow-up will be compared and investigated.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
